vote.title: 9. Appropriation Adjustment for the Walnut Street Urban Greening Project
vote.description:
Recommended Action: Approve an appropriation adjustment to recognize 
$2,199,000 in Clean California Local Grant Program funding from the California 
Department of Transportation for the Walnut Street Urban Greening project into 
the Parks Capital Grant-PWA, State Grant -Direct revenue account and appropriate 
the same amount into the Parks Capital Grant-PWA, Improvements Other Than 
Buildings expenditure account. (Requires five affirmative votes)
